BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State African American Cultural Center
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Student Life,Information Session
DESCRIPTION:The African American Cultural Center will host Real Talk on Lov
 e\, Sex and Safety\, an opportunity for the NC State community to have an h
 onest conversation about sex\, protection\, hookup culture\, consent and em
 otional safety in a fun and engaging way. Please complete the registration 
 form if you plan to attend. Registrants will get food and a goodie bag.
